<tr style="text-align:center;">
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Preceded&#160;by<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">"<a href="Magic_(Olivia_Newton-John_song)" title="Magic (Olivia Newton-John song)">Magic</a>" by <a href="Olivia_Newton-John" title="Olivia Newton-John">Olivia Newton-John</a></span></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b><a href="Billboard_Hot_100" title="Billboard Hot 100"><i>Billboard</i> Hot 100</a> <a href="List_of_number-one_hits_(United_States)" title="List of number-one hits (United States)">number-one single</a></b><br />
August 30, 1980 (1 week)</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">"<a href="Upside_Down" title="Upside Down">Upside Down</a>" by <a href="Diana_Ross" title="Diana Ross">Diana Ross</a></span></td>
