<tr style="text-align:center;">
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Preceded&#160;by<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">"<a href="Magic_(Olivia_Newton-John_song)" title="Magic (Olivia Newton-John song)">Magic</a>" by <a href="Olivia_Newton-John" title="Olivia Newton-John">Olivia Newton-John</a></span></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b>Canadian <a href="RPM_(magazine)" title="RPM (magazine)"><i>RPM</i></a> <a href="List_of_RPM_number-one_singles_of_1980" title="List of RPM number-one singles of 1980">number-one single</a></b><br />
October 11, 1980 – October 18, 1980 (2 weeks)</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
